{"tid":490740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬雲：90%網上評論無腦","createTime":"2017-12-06T01:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T13:19:09.000Z","uid":70985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cea11925eb130bc52f83fc16752681033ca889","tid":490740,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"人紅自然是非多，阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲也不例外。馬雲出席第四屆世界互聯網大會的論壇時表示，網上90%的評論都是沒腦，稱它們為「精神大便」，更指「現在沒有東亞病夫，只有網上病夫」。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲表示非常尊重新聞網站，所以從不干預任何媒體的任何運作，並指收購《南華早報》，是因為不希望媒體倒下和失去自我，更加不想令媒體因為錢而失去了客觀、理性。<br />\n他還對他在全世界擁有20多間豪宅的傳聞，表示「我也很好奇我在哪兒買了那麼多房子」，繼要說要用人工智能和大數據打擊假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171204/57540050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57540050&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSablsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=45b5803a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171204%2F57540050&h=ef5b5683\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171204/57540050</a>"},{"pid":"03ec4547cc463d6d6106a90629a8541be343fc5e","tid":490740,"uid":2189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"網民：90%馬雲評論無腦"},{"pid":"ed3a6eae688a5513a51f46a7762eeed0692f153a","tid":490740,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"低端？"},{"pid":"2a963d9a8e5026da69b4668c3b748c09a5cff1c6","tid":490740,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:55:16.000Z","msg":"條撚樣耍太極一流"},{"pid":"81c318df89785ccae02fab64493a03a1639963b5","tid":490740,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"佢又岩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c7443d7